==Spanish== 
===Etymology===
Old Spanish [[lejar]] (modern [[alejar]]) &gt; Latin ''[[laxare|laxāre]]'', influenced by [[dar]]

===Transitive verb=== 
'''dejar'''
# to [[leave]]
# to let go
# to [[abandon]]
# to [[allow]]
'''dejar de'''
# to [[stop]]; to [[cease]]; to [[quit]]

===Reflexive verb===
'''dejarse'''
# to allow oneself to be
# to [[leave]] [[behind]]; to [[forget]]
# to let oneself go
# to [[grow]]

